!.env.example

# packwiz override files that exceed GitHub's 100 MB blob limit. Both
# are CLIENT-side cosmetic assets shipped via the upstream CurseForge
# zip's overrides/ (custom main-menu animation + custom resource-pack
# ZIP). The server doesn't render either, so excluding them from the
# packwiz manifest only affects the client install. Also excluded from
# the packwiz index via packwiz/.packwizignore. PR 2's "publish Prism
# client zip" flow will need to source these separately (Git LFS,
# Release attachment, or download-at-build-time).
packwiz/config/fancymenu/assets/mahj_1294853429_mainmenu.fma
packwiz/config/openloader/resources/resources.zip
